T1  - Finite sample properties of estimators for autoregressive moving average models
AU  - Ansley, Craig F.
AU  - Newbold, Paul
JO  - Journal of Econometrics
VL  - 13
IS  - 2
SP  - 159
EP  - 183
PY  - 1980
DA  - 1980/06/01/
